*Deities: {{ill|lt=Amaterasu|Q455602|WD=Q455602|1=Amaterasu}}, {{ill|UNKNOWN|WD=Q1502690|lt=Takemikazuchi-no-Kami|1=Takemikazuchi}}, {{ill|WD=Q1107286|lt=Futsunushi-no-Kami|Q1107286|WD=Q1107286|1=Futsunushi}}, {{ill|lt=Ame-no-Koyane|UNKNOWN|lt=Ame-no-Koyane-no-Kami}}, Hime Ōkami<ref>{{Cite web|title=Urufushine Shrine|url=https://jinja-net.jp/uruhusine-jinja/|access-date=2025-9-27}}</ref>

