*Ōmiwa Shrine - deity: {{ill|UNKNOWN|WD=Q10936701|lt=Ōmononushi-no-Kami|1=Ōmononushi}}<ref>{{Cite book|和書 |title=History of Nabari City, Lower Volume |publisher=Nabari Local History Research Association |page=370}}</ref>

